snippet.title: X-Wing Trench Run - Virtual Reality [Full Gameplay]
snippet.description:
Project Stardust version 0.8 - Created by Dylan Stout at University of Utah. Download here: bit.ly/XWingVR_Latest 
Follow me on twitter: https://twitter.com/XWingVR 
This is a project under current development that attempts to research Virtual Reality Sickness in a fun way by recreating the 1983 coin-operated game "Star Wars" by Atari in full HD VR.
